Package: CARTEpigenoQC
Type: Package
Title: Quality Control Toolkit for CAR-T Single-Cell Epigenomic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kaitao Lai [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Kaitao Lai <your.email@example.com>
Description: A lightweight and extensible quality control toolkit for single-cell epigenomic data in CAR-T cell studies. Supports scATAC-seq, scCUT&Tag, scBS-seq. Computes FRiP scores, CAR insertion site coverage, and generates HTML/PNG reports.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    data.table,
    ggplot2,
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    rmarkdown,
    DT,
    gridExtra,
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
